snippet: McLaren Racing chief executive Jost Capito is set to follow Ron Dennis out of the Formula One team, the BBC and Autosport.com reported on Monday....
lead_paragraph: McLaren Racing chief executive Jost Capito is set to follow Ron Dennis out of the Formula One team, the BBC and Autosport.com reported on Monday.

headline.main: Chief Executive Capito Set to Leave McLaren: Reports
headline.print_headline: Chief Executive Capito Set to Leave McLaren: Reports
